Subject: [PATCH] drm: Remove pending_read_domains and pending_write_domain
Git-commit: e6090cc9be15f8e3a5e736d427186e39fea7cceb
Patch-mainline: v4.14-rc1
References: FATE#322643 bsc#1055900

The last user of these (i915.ko) no longer does. We can slim down the
core GEM object by removing the unused 8 bytes.

